name: KRYPTON
description:
December 21st 3109, Krypton founded in a vast freezing Alaskan earth. The Krypton bearing the telltale mineral inclusion came from a mine and formed at depths greater than 660 kilometers, the upper boundary of Earth’s lower mantle. Using analytical techniques including X-ray diffraction, X-ray fluorescence imaging and infrared spectroscopy.
